<p>Hero banner displays a large heading, some intro text and a call to action. A large background image is recommended.</p>

<h2>Background image</h2>

<p>The background image must follow a tight recipe so that it can be positioned reliably across a variety of devices. Use the Photoshop template to generate new banners that follow this same recipe.</p>

<ul>
<li><a href="#">Hero banner Photoshop template</a></li>
</ul>

<p><img src="{{asset "images/cta/cta-template.jpg"}}" style="width:100%;max-width:992px;"></p>



<h2>Rules</h2>

<ul>
	<li>Background images should be <code>1905px</code> x <code>362px</code></li>
  <li>Background images should be created with with this Photoshop template</li>
</ul>

<h2>Syntax</h2>

<div class="pattern-source">{{> hero-banner}}</div>

<h2>Options</h2>

<ul>
	<li>By default there is no background image, you'll need to supply this by attaching inline style on <code>&lt;div class="hero-banner"&gt;</code>. For example:
    <code>&lt;div class="hero-banner" style="background-image: url(path/to/image.jpg)"&gt;</code>.</li>
</ul>
